'''''Boba Fett vs. The Empire''''' was a proposed comic to be written by [[Tom Veitch]]. Its plot would have been centered around [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] being hired to apprehend [[Umak Leth]] after the latter betrays the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="Galaxy">{{CollectorCite|4|ComicScan|ComicScan: Comics That Almost Were}}</ref>

